# IMPORTANT: Keep essential data directories for ChromaDB and caching
# The following directories contain critical application data:
# - OUTPUT_DATA2/embeddings/ (ChromaDB collection with embeddings)
# - chromadb_storage/ (ChromaDB persistence layer)
# - data/textbooks/ (Course data and configurations)
# - data/exported_data/ (Processed document exports)
# - data/ocr_cache/ (OCR processing cache)
# These directories are INCLUDED in the Docker image for functionality

# Only exclude temporary/log subdirectories within data directories
OUTPUT_DATA2/progress_report/
data/temp/
data/logs/
run_logs/

# Backup files
*.bak
*.backup
*~

